This pattern computes the greatest common divisor of two numbers using Euclid's subtraction algorithm.

STITCH GUIDE:

stitch gcdstep = (
    over
    pick 1
    >
    if
        swap
        over
        hdc
        swap
    else
        over
        hdc
    end
)

INSTRUCTIONS:

ch 48, ch 18
* gcdstep * repeat while
sc yo, then fo
